params.markdown:
## Azure AI Foundry Guardrails

TThe Guardrails API requests are monitored when accessed via the Azure API Management service. This dashboard provides insights into:

- Guardrails API requests and average latency
- Prompt & completions risk categories
- Error rates
- Filtered content source
